    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly looking and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, factory-fresh state with no signs of use. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously stored and maintained to the highest standards. A rare find for a collector or a buyer seeking a like-new experience, this vehicle requires nothing but a new owner to appreciate its exceptional state.",
